title: Sleep Is Death - Geisterfahrer v16 - Full
description:
A storytelling game for two players by Jason Rohrer

Full download from (sleepisdeath.net) - Includes all executables and graphics packs.

Sleep Is Death is available from (http://sleepisdeath.net)
For a minimum donation of $1.75 you can support Jason Rohrer and
his other projects. (http://hcsoftware.sourceforge.net/jason-rohrer/)

-======-

Compiling from source
Make sure you have dev packages of the following libraries installed:

    libsdl
    libpng
    zlib 

The included "runToBuild" script should build the game for you automatically.

-======-
